Knesel Street (center, from left to right), adjoining the N.E. corner of Rossville Avenue, showing the site to be an empty lot. The view is northward across Knesel Street from an empty lot on the south side. The house shown fronts on Morris Street.

April 30, 1929.

P. L. Speer
